{"type":"message","id":"adbad0ef","parentId":"632a6d55","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:49:18.787Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-07 11:49:06 GMT+8] Feishu[kiit] DM | ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb [msg:om_x100b5273a5c2eca4b3fcc20886ef7df]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5273a5c2eca4b3fcc20886ef7df\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-07 11:49 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb\"\n}\n```\n\nOpenSpace 自我进化引擎你看看这个skill 对你帮助大吗？"}],"timestamp":1775533758771}}
{"type":"message","id":"6126d3f8","parentId":"adbad0ef","timestamp":"2026-04-07T03:49:29.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to look at a skill called \"OpenSpace 自我进化引擎\" and evaluate if it would be helpful to me. Let me search for this skill in the available skills list.\n\nLooking at the available skills, I don't see any skill with that name directly listed. But the user might be referring to something they want me to find or install. Let me check ClawHub for this skill, or maybe it's a reference to the self-improvement skill.\n\nActually, the user might be asking about a skill that could help with \"self-evolution\" or self-improvement. The closest skill I see is \"self-improvement\" which captures learnings, errors, and corrections for continuous improvement.\n\nLet me read the self-improvement skill to see if it matches what they're talking about, and also check if there's an OpenSpace skill on ClawHub.\n\n\nI should look into what \"OpenSpace 自我进化引擎\" actually refers to—it could be a specific skill available on ClawHub that I need to search for, or it might be something related to the self-improvement capabilities I'm already familiar with.","thinkingSignature":"09e87e41e42360926acec68a80c8503fbb18211b706c15a23c005f6b17bb0b85"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_puz4mm4qshuz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub search \"OpenSpace 自我进化引擎\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"clawhub not found or search failed\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":12995,"totalTokens":13302,"cost":{"input":0.0000105,"output":0.00032639999999999996,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.004873125,"total":0.005210025}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775533758846,"responseId":"0623b1c0ea47a66db96e982d89db0158"}}
